==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: One house, big and small.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī jīa dà xĭao

===Idiom===
'''[[一]][[家]][[大]][[小]]'''

# The whole family

#: ''[[放假]][[了]][[我们]]'''一家大小'''[[往]][[乡下]][[去]][[探望]][[祖母]]。 (([[Simplified Chinese]]))

#: ''[[放假]][[了]]，[[我們]]'''一家大小'''[[往]][[鄉下]][[去]][[探望]][[祖母]]。'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])

